name: microcosm - 1
description:
The microcosm images and videos are just curious explorations to the hidden world revealed under the microscope. It's amazing how much different everything when magnified larger hundreds of times. This ,I believe was a small rock.

I use on my main works a lot of inspiration from nature's shapes: rocks, branches, roots of a tree and so on. These smaller surface details and colors are great addition to the overall inspiration arsenal that I can benefit from.
